{"tid":1263270,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊叫樓下間餐廳嘅電視改播其他台","createTime":"2019-06-28T05:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T10:42:33.000Z","uid":254330,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eecc74107785ed44f76ad0ae43eae22bb097f0ba","tid":1263270,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:43:18.000Z","msg":"好多餐廳都有部電視比人睇<br />\n主要都係播CCTVB嘅81/83台<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">間接令班食客睇CCTVB偏頗嘅報導</span><br />\n<br />\n如果你係樓下or番工附近間餐廳嘅熟客，可以試下叫佢轉台！唔要CCTVB<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係lunch time 時段效果尤其顯著！</span><br />\n<br />\n食熟左，同個老細講轉其他台，應該都唔係好難嘅事，<span style=\"color: red;\">重點係要減少CCTVB嘅受眾！</span>"},{"pid":"20ef955ef4d726a5666425f379ac0899dbbef384","tid":1263270,"uid":254330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EFa21v5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEFa21v5.png&h=fa05b7d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ndone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9396a267ab7ab861572729de08d95ced0410b79","tid":1263270,"uid":12034,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 真係好戇鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係當左你就是天下"},{"pid":"fca57a614eab5aa1a9c45ccedec7a1b3b8303a6c","tid":1263270,"uid":186323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9396a267ab7ab861572729de08d95ced0410b79","tid":1263270,"uid":12034,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 真係好戇鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係當左你就是天下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:29:10.000Z","msg":"球星嚟講 你個樣就戇鳩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d1899