314431.pdf&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=2d6df72f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n交表<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=75a26f29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試<br />\n<br />\n免費傳真方法 <br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=f87ace0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a>"},{"pid":"444cbf3d8ed678a0efd3ff2f6255dacd455e3444","tid":1263270,"uid":254330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9396a267ab7ab861572729de08d95ced0410b79","tid":1263270,"uid":12034,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 真係好戇鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係當左你就是天下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:33:40.000Z","msg":"叫餐廳轉台就已經係我天下<br />\n咁叫餐廳service我係咩"},{"pid":"0d47fd9f6705f314e241b78e0e443bfcfb67bbd0","tid":1263270,"uid":254330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:40:26.000Z","msg":"唔止餐廳茶記，Salon都可以 客氣咁叫堆自己熟嘅舖頭轉台就得"},{"pid":"26b68df902b7a1bc9ddcb66249e6eeda5f046518","tid":1263270,"uid":447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28